item.title: Exaustion
item.description: I fret about the past, While impatient of my future, And there is exhaustion at the present, With many ongoing venture. I wish I did this Or am I doing it correct? Or how will I do it? Anyways, to drain is the answer. Every capability in comparison with our potential, unpolished with rusty characteristics No one ever interested in a rat-race, Yet many end up as statistics. I don’t think this ever comes to an end,

item.title: A Thought Undefined
item.description: The thought of you brings tears sometimes I really don’t know how one could invade. the Tier 0 space in my heart. Usually I can let go off any distraction, Be it a crush or be it any soul, And shift my focus at daily chore. But recently I am proving it all wrong, As I write this to be a poem or sing this to be a song A thought which I’m trying to define,

item.title: About
item.description: An ambitious Girl from India, She has a vision to see A computer engineering degree, To use her skills to solve problems free. Started to explore finance, To understand the numbers and trends, Started to build applications, For a better future she intends. With a knack for technology, The future looks bright and sunny, A career of excellence, A real engineer of money. She will make it with her own might,

item.title: If it is meant to be, will it be?
item.description: 2 years of hard work gave me unexpected results, No they weren’t positive. I needed an exotic fruit, but those results gave me rotten smell, Disappointed me, thought it was unfair. Never was I ever so stressed, That I Felt every decision of mine went down the hill, When all I could hope for is to get some Will. Now after several months I realize, Maybe I was insane to choose a harder way,

item.title: Happy Birthday Julie!
item.description: Happy Birthday to You…(2) Happy Birthday dear Julie Happy Birthday to You During initial Engineering blues, I hoped to get a good crew, I had a glimpse when I met you, That you’d be part of it too! And now that we have walked through, By the four different avenues, I wish the best for you, In your future endeavors too! May Deloitte be great to you, For your work life break through,

item.title: Definition of Fun
item.description: At an age group with Netflix binges, counterfeits and heartaches, I found a pendant carrying dreams, failures and responsibility as a Load. It preferred Late night Hustles, Many coffee cups and Limited breaks, As its eyes stuck through many bugs in the Code. “Bro why don’t you have some Fun?” is the most frequent Question, where Having no Regrets is all that she really wants - Said One Direction. Maybe the clubbers found it boring and a regret for missing out a moment,

item.title: Friends through a 4-year sail...
item.description: It’s long time that I wrote an Essay. I’ll try my best with a poem to portray. Past were the days when my parents were fed up with their career And therefore with their advice I chose to be an engineer It’s the story of my first year when I didn’t know where to start, I didn’t know how will I end, Maybe taking up Engineering was an Art And I ’ll pat myself and commend.
